flowchart LR
    REQ[Inbound HTTP request] --> WAF[WAF ModSecurity]
    WAF --> CID[Correlation-ID plugin]
    CID --> JWT[JWT plugin Keycloak JWKS]
    JWT --> OPA[OPA governance plugin]
    OPA --> RL[Rate limiting Redis quota]
    RL --> ACL[ACL tenant-service]
    ACL --> LOG[Kong logging plugin]
    LOG --> API[FastAPI backend trusted headers]

    style WAF fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626
    style JWT fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb
    style OPA fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706
    style RL fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#db2777
    style API fill:#d1fae5,stroke:#059669
